<SampleDescription>
    <p>This sample depicts the 2016 presidential election results in the United States. In addition, an interactive legend is added to the top of the map.</p>
</SampleDescription>
<ActionDescription>
    <p>In this example, you can see how to apply different styles to a shape in the map when it is clicked or hovered with the mouse. The selection is enabled by the <a target='_blank' class='code' href='https://help.syncfusion.com/cr/blazor/Syncfusion.Blazor.Maps.MapsLayerSelectionSettings.html' aria-label="Class reference of MapsLayerSelectionSettings">MapsLayerSelectionSettings</a>, and the highlight is enabled by the <a target='_blank' class='code' href='https://help.syncfusion.com/cr/blazor/Syncfusion.Blazor.Maps.MapsLayerHighlightSettings.html' aria-label="Class reference of MapsLayerHighlightSettings">MapsLayerHighlightSettings</a>.</p>
    <p>More information about selection and highlight can be found in this <a target='_blank' href='https://blazor.syncfusion.com/documentation/maps/user-interactions' aria-label="Blazor Maps User Interaction documentation" >documentation section</a>.</p>
</ActionDescription>

<div class="control-section">
    <SfMaps Theme="@Theme" Background="transparent">
        <MapsAreaSettings Background="transparent" />
        <MapsTitleSettings Text="USA Election Results - 2016">
            <MapsTitleTextStyle Size="16px" FontFamily="Segoe UI" />
        </MapsTitleSettings>
        <MapsLegendSettings Visible="true" Mode="LegendMode.Interactive" Position="LegendPosition.Top" Width="80%">
            <MapsLegendTextStyle FontWeight="400" Size="14px" FontFamily="Segoe UI" />
        </MapsLegendSettings>
        <MapsZoomSettings Enable="false" />
        <MapsLayers>
            <MapsLayer ShapeData='new {dataOptions = SampleService.WebAssetsPath + "data/maps/usa.json"}' ShapeDataPath="State" ShapePropertyPath="@ShapePropertyPath" DataSource="@SelectionDataSource" TValue="SelectionData">
                <MapsLayerTooltipSettings Visible="true" ValuePath="State">
                    <MapsLayerTooltipTextStyle FontFamily="Segoe UI"></MapsLayerTooltipTextStyle>
                </MapsLayerTooltipSettings>
                <MapsLayerHighlightSettings Enable="true" Fill="#A3B0D0" />
                <MapsLayerSelectionSettings Enable="true" Fill="#4C515B" Opacity="1" />
                <MapsShapeSettings ColorValuePath="Candidate">
                    <MapsShapeBorder Width="1" Color="white" />
                    <MapsShapeColorMappings>
                        <MapsShapeColorMapping Value="Trump" Color="@TrumpColor" />
                        <MapsShapeColorMapping Value="Clinton" Color="@ClintonColor" />
                    </MapsShapeColorMappings>
                </MapsShapeSettings>
            </MapsLayer>
        </MapsLayers>
    </SfMaps>
    <div class="urllink">
        Source:
        <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/United_States_presidential_election,_2016" target="_blank">en.wikipedia.org</a>
    </div>
</div>

